name: Model HQ
address: P349+VHW, Gesing, Banjar, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81152, Indonesia
review 1:
What an amazing day and sunset evening we all had. The Cacao ceremony and the magic fire dance act made the night even more unforgettable. It’s a pity you can’t go in easy and have to be recomend by someone unless you know the owner “The Model” himself to get a smooth entrance. Looking forward to get invited again to the best (kept) secret party from Bali.
Ps. The animal show of Tiger and Lion where unbelievable same as the 12 meter hight acrobatic on the rope show.
Please invite us again 🙏🏽🙏🏽🙏🏽
